Fourth Department,

September, 1952.

(September 24, 1952.) Homer L. Householder, Respondent, v. Town of Grand Island, Erie County, Appellant.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, with $10 costs. Present — Taylor, P. J., McCurn, Vaughan, Kimball and Piper, JJ. [See ante, p. 874.]
